(1, 60, 'GII THIU', 'gi-i-thi-u', '<h4></h4>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Thng 12/2011, ForumTrkibadmin.comc thnh lp, y lwebsite cung cp nhng thng tin chuyn nghip v tin tc v din n cu lng.Nhn thy s pht trin ca cu lng trong nc, bn cnh  l mong mun phc v tt hn cho thnh vin v nhng bn yu mn cu lng. Thng 12/2012, Ban Qun Tr Vnbadminton  mnh dn xy dng Shop cu lng VNB (<a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/\">/</a>)  c th lm c vai tr ny. Vi kinh nghim nhiu nm hot ng trong lnh vc cu lng, n vi shopvnb bn s yn tm v cht lng sn phm, i ng t vn sn phm chuyn nghip v gi c hp l.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Bn cnh mt website chuyn nghip th ShopTrkibadmin cn pht trin thm 1 knh fanpage<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/caulongvnbadminton/\">https://www.facebook.com/caulongvnbadminton/</a> cung cp thng tin nhanh hn cho thnh vin yu mn cu lng. Chnh s chuyn nghip ny  c to c uy tn rt ln trong cng ng yu mn cu lng trong v ngoi nc.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Hin nay, H thng ca hng cu lng Trkibadmin  chn 50 chi nhnh tri di trn khp mi min t nc. Vitiu ch lun m bo cung cp y  cc mt hng chuyn dng dnh ring cho b mn cu lng nh giy, vt cu lng, ti vt, balo, qun o, ph kin,... ni tri vi nhiu phn khc gi tri di t thp n caonn cc lng th cn mua g c n ngay vi ShopVNB, chc chn s lm cc bn v cng hi lng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">ShopVNB lun l ni cung cp nhanh nht cc mt hng hot n t nhngthng hiu top u th gii nh Yonex, Lining, Victor, Mizuno,... Khng nhng vy cc sn phm n t cc hng tm trung v gi r nh Adidas, Forza, Apacs, VNB, Kamito,... Shop cu lng Trkibadmin cng lun cung cp y  v mu m rt a dng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">* c bit, ShopTrkibadmin l a ch ni ting cng vt cu lng chunnht  Vit Nam. Tt c cc ca hng c trang b my an vt in t cao cp cng nhn vin  shoplun c trau di lin tc cc k thut an vt hng u trn th gii.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>TM NHN, S MNH V GI TR CT LI</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>TM NHN</strong>: \"Tr thnh nh phn phi v sn xut th thao ln nht Vit Nam\"</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Tr thnh n v dn u c nc trong lnh vc th thao, gip nng cao sc khe cng ng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- T lc sn xut cc sn phm cht lng cao, ph hp vi nhu cu ca ngi Vit.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Xy dng h thng ca hng rng khp 64 tnh thnh.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>S MNH</strong>: \"Trkibadmin SPORTS cam kt mang n nhng sn phm, dch v cht lng tt nht phc v cho ngi chi th thao  nng cao sc khe ca chnh mnh.\"</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>i vi th trng</strong>: Tr thnh Thng hiu cu lng ca ngi Vit, cung cp nhng sn phm cu lng cht lng tt nht, p ng nhu cu luyn tp cu lng v chm sc sc khe ca mi ngi.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>i vi i tc</strong>:  cao tinh thn hp tc cng pht trin; c gng tr thnh Ngi ng hnh s 1 ca cc i tc.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>i vi nhn vin</strong>: Xy dng mi trng lm vic chuyn nghip, nng ng, sng to v nhn vn; to iu kin thu nhp cao v c hi pht trin cng bng cho tt c nhn vin.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>i vi x hi</strong>: Hi ha li ch doanh nghip vi li ch x hi; ng gp tch cc vo cc hot ng hng v cng ng, th hin tinh thn trch nhim cng dn v nim t ho dn tc.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>GI TR CT LI: TRUNG - TN - TM - TR -NHN</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>TRUNG</strong>: Trung thc vi Khch hng - i tc - Nhn vin. Thc hin ng cc ch  u i, dch v hu mi  cam kt, t quyn li ca ngi tiu dng ln trn ht, chn thnh tip thu mi  kin ng gp.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>TN</strong>: Trkibadmin SPORTS t ch TN ln hng u, ly ch TN lm trng tm i vi Khch hng - i tc - Nhn vin. VNB SPORTS lun n lc ht mnh  m bo ng v cao hn cc cam kt ca mnh i vi khch hng, i tc; c bit l cam kt v cht lng- sn phm - dch v.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>TM</strong>: Trkibadmin SPORTS t ch TM l mt trong nhng nn tng quan trng ca vic kinh doanh. Coi trng khch hng v lun ly khch hng lm trung tm, t li ch v mong mun ca khch hng ln hng u; n lc mang n cho khch hng nhng sn phm - dch v tt nht; xem s hi lng ca khch hng l thc o thnh cng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Tr</strong>: Trkibadmin SPORTS lun  cao s sng to, l n by pht trin, nhm to ra gi tr khc bit v bn sc ring ca sn phm. Chng ti  cao tinh thn dm ngh, dm lm, khuyn khch tm ti, ng dng tin b khoa hc, k thut v cng ngh mi vo qun l, sn xut; lun ch ng ci tin, nng cao cht lng sn phm- dch v.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>NHN</strong>: Trkibadmin SPORTS xy dng cc mi quan h vi khch hng, i tc, ng nghip v x hi bng s thin ch, tinh thn nhn vn. Chng ti lun coi ngi lao ng l ti sn qu gi nht; xy dng mi trng lm vic chuyn nghip, nng ng, sng to; to iu kin thu nhp cao v c hi pht trin cng bng cho tt c cn b nhn vin.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Khu hiu (slogan)</strong>: Together we can</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>TRIT L KINH DOANH</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Trkibadmin SPORTS mong mun tr thnh mt cng ty phn phi v sn xut sn phm cu lng cht lng tt nht  Vit Nam. V th chng ti tm nim rng cht lng v sng to l ngi bn ng hnh ca Trkibadmin SPORTS. Chng ti xem khch hng l trung tm v cam kt p ng mi nhu cu ca khch hng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Chnh sch cht lng</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Lun tha mn v c trch nhim vi khch hng bng cch khng ngng ci tin, a dng ha sn phm v dch v, m bo cht lng vi gi c cnh tranh, tn trng o c kinh doanh v tun theo php lut.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>* ShopTrkibadmin cam kt bn hng chnh hng, khng bn hng km cht lng lm nh hng n thnh vin.</strong></span></p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-11-15 07:13:51', 67, '', '2023-11-15 07:13:51', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-11-15 07:13:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 10, '', '', 1, 29, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(2, 61, 'Hng dn thanh ton', 'hu-ng-d-n-thanh-toan', '<p><strong>1. i vi qu khch hng mua hng trc tip ti cc chi nhnh</strong></p>\r\n<p>- Tt c cc chi nhnh ca h thng Trkibadmin u chp thun thanh ton bng tin mt, chuyn khon qua ngn hng hoc thanh ton qua th tn dng. i vi thanh ton qua th tn dng (Trkibadmin Sports chu ph th)  bt c chi nhnh no ca h thng ca hng cu lng Trkibadmin.</p>\r\n<p>- Qu khch c th n trc tip chi nhnh hoc lin h qua hotline chi nhnh  bit thm chi tit.</p>\r\n<p>- Qu khch vui lng kim tra sn phm k trc khi thanh ton.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. i vi qu khch hng mua hng online t hng qua Website</strong></p>\r\n<p>- Sau khi nhn c thng tin t hng chng ti s gi in  xc nhn n hng trong vng 24h v phn hi li thng tin cho khch hng v vic thanh ton v thi gian giao nhn.</p>\r\n<p>- Qu khch c th thanh ton COD - thanh ton khi nhn hng, hoc chuyn khon thanh ton trc qua ti khon ngn hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Trong trng qu khch mua sn phm vt c yu cu an sn cc, qu khch vui lng thanh ton trc ton b gi tr n hng bao gm vt v cc an vt bng hnh thc chuyn khon qua ti khon ngn hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Qu khch c th kim tra hng trc khi nhn hng, trong trng hp c yu cu i/tr hng hoc vn  v sn phm, qu khch vui lng lin h li qua hotline0866779560 c h tr.</p>\r\n<p><strong>3. i vi qu khch hng mua hng online t hng qua s hotline ca chi nhnh</strong></p>\r\n<p>- Qu khch c th thanh ton COD - thanh ton khi nhn hng, hoc chuyn khon thanh ton trc qua ti khon ngn hng.</p>\r\n<p>- Trong trng qu khch mua sn phm vt c yu cu an sn cc, qu khch vui lng thanh ton trc ton b gi tr n hng bao gm vt v cc an vt bng hnh thc chuyn khon qua ti khon ngn hng (Danh sch s ti khon ca tng chi nhnh c cp nht bn di).</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. i vi qu khch hng mua s</strong></p>\r\n<p>i vi nhng khch hng c nhn hoc ca hng mun lin h mua s ( bn bun)lin h s: 0866779560. S c nhn vin h tr.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-11-15 07:24:36', 67, '', '2023-11-15 07:30:43', 67, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-11-15 07:24:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\