(3, 62, 'Hng dn cch chn vt cu lng cho ngi mi chi', 'hu-ng-d-n-cach-ch-n-v-t-c-u-long-cho-ngu-i-m-i-choi', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">i vi ngi mi chi, vic la chn mt cyvt cu lng tt vph hp vi bn thn l mt chuyn khng phi d dng. Hiu c iu ny, SHOPTrkibadmin  pht trin 1tnh nngc th gip cho ngi michi cu lng c thla chn cyvt cu lngtheo nhngyu t nh: Thng hiu; thng s vt cu lng(trng lng, im cn bng,  cng); theo phong cch chi (tn cng, phng th, cng th ton din), theo ni dung chi,trnh  cng nh mc gi. Bnch cn bmchn nhng thng s ph hp vi bn,Trkibadmins la chn nhng cy vt cu lng chnh hng p ng nhng yu cu ca bn a ra.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"layout-collection\">\r\n<div class=\"block-collection col-12\">\r\n<div class=\"section-box-bg\">\r\n<div class=\"category-products\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1. Gii thiu vt cu lngFelet Velton (Grey) chnh hng</strong></span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vy l bn c th d dng la chn cho mnh mt cy vt cu lng tt v ng  ri phi khng?</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Tuy nhin,  hiu r hn v cch chn vt cu lng cho ngi mi chiv v cc thng s   cp trn, hy cng SHOPVNBphn tch tng yu t a ra l do ti sao chng ta li la chn vt cu lng nh vy. By gi chng ta cng tm hiu nh.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1. Cch chn vt cu lng cho ngi mi chi theo THNG HIU:</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Hin nay, trn th trng c rt nhiu thng hiu (hng) vt cu lng  mi ngi c th la chn. C nhng thng hiu vt cu lng cao cp phi k n nh Yonex, Victor, Lining..vv hay nhng hng vt cu lng gi r cho hc sinh, sinh vin nh apacs, proacehay VNB. Vy, sn phm n t nhng thng hiu ny c c g khc bit v nn chn vt cu lng n t hng no? Cng ShopTrkibadmin phn tch k hn nh!</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1.1 Hng vt cu lng ni ting nht th gii  Yonex</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Nhc n vt cu lng th khng th khng nhc n ng ln Yonex. Hng cu lng ln nht th gii v sn lng vt bn ra v c rt nhiu tn tui vn ng vin ln s dng. ng thi Yonex cn l nh ti tr ln cho cc gii u trn ton th gii l i tc quan trng ca lin on cu lng th gii.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">u im ln nht ca hng vt cu lng Yonex ny  chnh l lun i tin phong trong nhng pht minh v cng ngh trn nhng cy vt. Ngoi ra cn i u trong thit k vi nhng sn phm c mu sc ni bt, khung vt c cu trc c bit ph hp vi nhiu li chi v tng i tng khc nhau.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Cc cy vt m hng Yonex cho ra mt th trng u l cc sn phm cht lng, mang tnh n nh v tc  kinh ngc. Dn u v cng ngh sn xut, cho nn cc cy vt u ca Yonex u c trang b cc cng ngh hin i nht. Hu nh cc cy vt ca cc vn ng vin top ca bng xp hng u l mang thng hiu Yonex.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt s sn phm mi nht ca hng vt cu lng ni ting Yonex mi cho ra th trng nh: Vt Cu Lng Yonex Astrox 77 pro, Vt Cu Lng Yonex Arcsaber 11 Pro, astrox 99,...iu cho nhng nh gi, phn hi rt tch cc t ngi chi.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Tuy nhin, nhc im ca nhng cy vt n t thng hiu vt cu lng Yonex l gi thnh kh cao, nhng dng vt cao cao cp c th ln n 2-3 triu. Kh t  so vi nhu cu ca hc sinh, sinh vin.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1.2 Thng hiu vt cu lng Victor</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Nu nh trc y Victor c xem l th lc ln trong cc hng vt cu lng trn th gii th gi y hng vn duy tr c iu . Ging nh Yonex cc vt cu lng ca Victor cng c nhiu vt th ni ting s dng nh: Gao Ning, Yang Wei, v Zhang Ji Wen.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Phn ln cc sn phm m Victor cho ra mt u hng ti ngi s dng c sc mnh, h tr cc c p cu v phn cng chp nhong. Mt s cy vt lm bng graphit cacbon, l mt cy vt bn, chnh xc dnh cho c nhng ngi chi kinh nghim v mi lm quen.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Tuy nhin, trong vi nm nay tr li y th hng Victor li tung ra th trng kh t vt cu lng mi so vi nhng tn tui cn li nh Yonex hay Lining.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1.3Vt cu lng thng hiu Li-Ning</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Hng vt cu lng ni ting ny chuyn sn xut cc dng c th thao,  tp th thao ln ca Trung Quc v sn phm ph kin cu lng l 1 trong nhng dng sn phm trng im ca hng Lining.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">L mt thng hiu n t Trung Quc nhng khng v th thng hiu vt cu lng Lining khng c cho n  Vit Nam. Lining ngy cng chim c nhiu cm tnh ca ngi dng v ang ngy cng pht trin. Dn nm v th s 2 th gii v tham vng vt qua Yonex.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vt cu lng Lining c cc nc s dng rt nhiu, c bit  cc quc gia ca Chu . Vt Lining em li tri nghim kh mi l cho cc anh em mi gia nhp mn th thao ny.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Cc sn phm vt cu lng Lining ni tri vi mu m a dng c chia thnh nhiu dng vt khc nhau ph hp vi tng li chi nh aeronaut, calibar, tectonic... c bit hng vt cu lng ni ting ny cn rt tr trng vo thit k mu sc v ngoi hnh cho cy vt.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vt cu lng Lining trn th trng ang c rt nhiu ngi chi a chung, t bit s c nhiu phn khc vt cu lng t 1 triu n 2 triu. Mt trong s  phi k n nh Vt Cu Lng Lining Aeronaut 6000, Aeronaut 6000 speed, Aeronaut 6000C, Vt Cu Lng Lining Aeronaut 4000c, Vt Cu Lng Lining Calibar 300C Chnh Hng..</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1.4Thng hiu vt cu lngMizuno</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Hng vt cu lng Mizuno cng xut pht t Nht Bn, hin cng l 1 trong nhng thng hiu c a chung trn th trng. Mizuno ra i cng kh lu so vi cc hng ln khc nh Yonex, Lining hay Victor.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Nhng cy vt cu lng Mizuno tr trng vo cht liu cao cp v hnh dng khung vt c l nhng vn cng nng v cho tnh kh ng hc cao.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Hin nay trn th trng Vit Nam, Mizuno  c ch ng vng chc bi nhng cy vt cu lng Mizuno ni bt vi thit k cao cp t cht liu ti mc  hon thin sn phm.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Nhc im, gi thnh cc cy vt cu lng Mizuno lun  mc tng i cao nu em so v gi vi cc cy vt ca hng vt cu lng khc.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt s cy vt ca mizuno c a chung phi k n nh: Vt cu lng Mizuno Speedflex 9.1, Vt cu lng Mizuno Fortius 50 Spirit, Vt cu lng Mizuno Fortius 30 Controll...</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1.5 Vt cu lng thng hiu Proace</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Ngoi nhng tn tui ni ting v ang rt c a chung k trn; vi nhng mu vt v cng t  th cng c nhiu hng vt gi r  p ng nhu cu cho ngi chi phong tro, hc sinh, sinh vin. Tiu biu phi k n hng vt cu lng proace.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vt cu lng Proace l thng hiu ca Anh thnh lp vo nm 1978. Hng lun n lc cung cp cc thit b h tr cc b mn th thao nh golf, Tennis, cu lng. Vi mong mun em n cc sn phm cht lng. Tnh n nay vt cu lng Proace  nhn c rt nhiu li tn dng v uy tn v sn phm cht lng.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mc d khng to ra nhiu cy vt s 1 th gii nh hng Yonex nhng Proace cng  cho ra i nhiu sn phm vt cu lng ni ting nh Proace S.D.S,..</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vt cu lng Proace  cao cht lng sn phm, chnh v vy m bn c th thy c nhng cy vt Proace c th s dng t i ny sang i khc m vn c th s dng tt. Mt c im duy nht m cho ti thi im hin ti c nhn mnh thy ch c Proace lm c iu ny.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1.6 Hng Vt cu lng gi r Apacs</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Ni tip hng vt cu lng gi r l thng hiu vt cu lng Apacs. Mt thng hiu hin cng ang c rt nhiu ngi chi la chn. Mt c im ni bt ca hng vt cu lng Apacs l cc cy vt ca h lun c s bn b, khung vt cng chu c mc cng ln v mu m a dng i cng vi gi thnh hp l.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt s cy vt cu lng Apacs ni bt c th k n nh: Apacs Z-Ziggler, Apacs Virtus 99</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Hng vt cu lng gi r ny c nhiu dng vt khc nhau trong  ni bt l dng Tantrum series vi li nh thin cng, dng vt Ziggler ph hp vi iu cu v phn tt, dng Lethal Light l dng thn nh, cho kh nng th cu tc  v chun xc.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Nhn chung, nu bn tm kim mt cu vt cu lng gi r cho ngi mi chi v c cht lng tt, mc cng cao; mu m a dng th hng vt cu lng Apacs ng  bn cn nhc.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>1.7 Vt cu lng mang thng hiu VNB</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt thng hiu xut pht t lng t ho dn tc. Vt cu lng mang thng hiu VNB  v ang lm ma lm gi trn th trng. Cc sn phm vt mng thng hiu VNB u c cc khch hng tin dng v nh gi cht lng. D l mt thng hiu vt trong nc nhng VNB khng lm anh em tht vng v hiu nng trn tng cy vt. VNB lun ci tin v em n cho cc anh em sn phm ti u nht vi mc gi phi chng nht. Thng hiu VNB ha hn s vn ra bin ln. Snh ngang vi cc thng hiu ni ting.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt trong nhng sn phm vt VNB phi k n l VNB V200 ( v200 xanh, v200  v v200i mu hng cho n), VNB V88, VBB TC88. Nhng sn phm vt cu lng VNB lun p ng tiu ch r, bn, p p ng nhu cu ca ngi mi chi v hc sinh, sinh vin.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Ngoi nhng hng vt cu lng ni ting Shop VNB va nu trn th cng c nhiu thng hiu khc nh prokenex, Kumpoo, Kawasaki, VS thuc phn khc vt cu lng gi r. Cng l nhng thng hiu ng tin cy cho s la chn ca bn.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>2. Cch chn vt cu lng cho ngi mi chitheo thng s vt</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Thng s vt cu lng l mt trong nhng yu t quan trng quyt nh n 1 cy vt cu lng c ph hp vi bn hay khng. Thng s vt cu lng thng s bao gm: Trng lng vt, im cn bng,  cng a vt, chu vi cn vt.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>2.1 Trng lng ca vt - Mt trong nhng kinh nghim chn vt cu lng cho ngi mi chi</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Bt k ai khi t vn cch chn vt cu lng cho bn, h cng s ni vi bn rng trng lng vt l yu t quan trng nht. Khng c trng lng tt nht m mi ngi s ph hp vi mt loi trng lng khc nhau. Nh sn xut s dng k hiu U trn thn vt gip ngi mua ch cn nhn thi cng c th bit c trng lng ca mi chic vt v phn bit c chng. Bn khng bit mi chi cu lng nn chn vt no? Gi  trng lng vt cho bn.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- 5U: khong 75g  80g.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- 4U: Khong 80g  85g.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- 3U: Khong 85g  90g.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- 2U: Khong 90g  95g.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Mi cc bn xem qua video  hiu r hn</strong>:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Tuy nhin, i vi ngi mi bit chi cu lng bn nn chn sn phm nng t 80 - 85g (cha k dy cc v cun cn) nh. Nhng chic vt ny khng qu nng cng khng qu nh nn s gip bn hn ch v gim tnh trng b mi tay v m bo  chnh xc khi nh cu. Mt cy vt nh l s la chn tt nht cho ngi mi bt u v n gip bn di chuyn nhanh cng nh cho bn nhiu thi gian  iu chnh chuyn ng ca vt.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>2.2 Chn  Cng/Mm ca thn vt va vi lc c tay</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Tc  vung vt chnh l th s quyt nh bn thch hp vi vt do hay vt cng. Mt thn vt cng s c kh nng phn hi nhanh v mnh, rt ph hp vi nhng ngi c tc  vung vt nhanh. N cho php bn tr li cc qu cu nhanh hn v gy nhiu bt ng cho i th. Thng nhng cy vt thn cng s i hi ngi chi c k thut cu lng tt nh VV bn chuyn, chuyn nghip, cc VV th gii.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt thn vt mm do (do khi vung, vt c  cong nht nh), bi v ngi mi chi luyn tp rt nhiu nn s cn vn  tr lc, gip gii phng hon ton lc c tay khi bn l mt ngi c tc  vung vt chm hoc l ngi mi bt u chi cu. Cch chn vt cu lng cho ngi mi chi khng s dngthn cng, nh vy s khin bn au tay v khng th pht huy tt tc dng nh cu lng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>2.3 im cn bng</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">im cn bng vt cu lng la mt trong nhng thng s vt ma ngi chi cu lng cn chu y khi t vn mua vt cu lng, cch chn vt cu lng cho ngi mi chi. im cn bng vt cu lng se quyt inh c  nng u, nhe u cua cy vt va ng nghia vi li chi tn cng, phong thu cua tng ngi chi.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Vt nh u</strong>: Cho kh nng linh hot v iu cu cao nhng hn ch  kh nng tn cng, ph hp vi cc c chn cu, y cu, chm cu.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Vt cn bng</strong>: H tr tt trong kh nng iu cu v trn li, tn cng cng tng i tt, thin v li nh cng th ton din.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Vt nng u</strong>: y l in hnh cho dng vt tn cng uy lc, ph hp vi cc c p, nh mnh, cu i su xung cui sn.Vt cng nng u th kh nng tn cng cng tt i hi theo n phi l  cng ca vt. Nhng ngc li th n cho kh nng linh hot km hn.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"></span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>3. Chn vt cu lng theo Phong cch chi</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Nh shop cng   cp v im cn bng  phn thng s vt bn trn, th cc bn cng  hnh dung c 1 cy vt thin cng hay cng th ton din th thng s vt s nh th no. Tuy Nhin, Shop VNB cng phn loi sn cho bn cc dng vt no thin cng; cng th ton din; hay phn tt, phng th.</span></p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>3.1 Chn vt cu lng cho ngi chi theo phong cch chi Tn Cng</strong></span></h3>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Li chi tn cng dn dp, Smash cu lin tc  ghi im, p o i th trn sn lun l li chi c rt nhiu cc lng th a thch. c bit, mt trong nhng yu t quyt nh to nn c p cu uy lc chnh l cy vt ca bn. Chnh v th vic la chn mt cy vt thin cng nng u s ph hp vi li nh cng ca bn. Mt trong s nhng cy vt thin cng phi k n nh:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Vt cu lng Yonex thin cng: Vt cu lng Yonex Astrox 99, Yonex Astrox 88D Pro, Yonex Astrox 77 Pro...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Vt cu lng Lining thin cng: Vt cu lng Lining Calibar 900C, Lining Tectonic 7C, 4000c,...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Vt cu lng Victor thin cng: Victor Thruster Ruyga, victor jetspeed 10,...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>3.2 Li chi Cng Th Ton Din</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Bn l ngi chi cu lng yu thch li nh k thut, nhanh, chm ty bin, thch kim sot cu, iu cu bo mn sc bn i th v cht h bng mt pha tn cng nhanh chp nhong. Bn l ngi mi chi cu lng v cha nh hnh c li nh ca mnh, cha bit lc tay cng nh phong cch chi ca mnh. Hay bn l ngi chi lc tn cng nhanh, dn dp, lc li phng th n nh t t, kim sot trn cu th c hn  l li nh cng th ton din hay cn gi l ton din.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Li nh cng th ton din khng ch da vo k thut, sc bn, kh nng phn on tnh hung cu ca ngi m quan trng khng km cn l cy vt m bn dng. Mt cy vt nng u cho kh nng tn cng rt tt nhng li hn ch trong vn  phn x nhanh ca cc pha cu cn li, cu nhanh. Mt cy vt nh u gip bn ng bin nhanh trong cc tnh hng cu i hng bt ng, nhng pha b nh, chp cu, y cu, chi trn li c thc hin rt hiu qu nhng kh nng tn cng ca vt li khng cao, p cu i khng cm, gy mt sc ngi chi. V vy, mt cy vt cn bng cho li chi cng th ton din l v cng quan trng quyt nh phn ln n li nh, phong cch chi v trnh  ngi chi.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vt cu lng ton din, hay cn gi l vt cu lng cn bng l vt c im cn bng 285 +- 3 mm hoc c hng xc nh n 285 +- 5 mm.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Ngy nay, cc hng cu lng sn xut vt ton din thng a vo cc dng vt ring m khi nhc n dng vt  ngi chi s bit y l cy vt ton din. V d nh:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Yonex: Arc Saber, Nanoflare, Doura, ...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Victor: Brave Sword, Hypernano X, Jetspeed, ...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Lining: High Carbon, nhng cy vt theo Boost Series, ...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Mizuno: Technoblade, ...</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>3.3 Cch chn vt cu lng theo li chi Phn Tt, Phng Th</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vt cu lng chuyn phn tt ni bt vi s nhanh l trong li chi, gip ngi chi c s linh hot trong phng th, bn cnh  cn dnh th ch ng t nhng pha phn tt cht lng.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt s cy vt thin v li nh phn tt, phng th phi k n:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Vt cu lng Yonex chuyn th phn tt: Arcsaber 11, Nanoflare 700 xanh.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Vt cu lng Victor: Brave Sword 12.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">- Vt cu lng Lining chuyn th: Aeronaut 6000D, Vt cu lng Lining 3D Calibar 300B, Lining 3D Calibar 900i.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>4. Chn vt cu lng theo ni dung chi</strong></span></h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Ni dung chi cu lng thng s chia ra 2 ni dung chnh  l nh i v nh n.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Vt cu lng c cn phn bit vt nh i v nh n hay khng? Tht s y cng l mt cu hi c kh nhiu ngi chi tm hiu. C nhiu bn chi th s s dng vt ring  nh i v nh n. Cn 1 s ngi chi th s dng 1 vt dng chung cho c nh n v nh i, min sao hp tay l c.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Tht s th cng cha c ci no quy nh r vt ch s dng ring cho nh i, hoc ch s dng ring cho nh n. Tuy nhin, trong nh i thng nhng pha cu cho tc  nhanh hn nn i hi chn la nhng cy vt c trng lng khng qu nng tm 4U, im cn bng hi nng u v a vt cng trung bnh  ngi chi c th d dng x l mi tnh hung trn sn u.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Mt s mu vt cu lng nh i: Yonex Nanoflare 700 , Yonex Astrox 88d pro, Mizuno JPX 8.1, Lining Tectonic 7.</span></p>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>5. Hng dn c