(7, 98, 'HNG DN PHT CU TRONG NH I', 'hu-ng-d-n-phat-c-u-trong-danh-doi', '<p>Trong luyn tp hay thi u cu lng th nh i l mt hnh thc kh ph bin. c bit vi nhng ngi chi phong tro th nh i l hnh thc ch yu vi mc ch gii tr rt cao. Trong nh i hay nh n th pht cu cng l mt k thut c bn v rt quan trng v c coi l s khi u ca t chc tn cng. Cht lng ca pht cu tt hay xu c nh hng trc tip n vic ginh quyn ch ng hay b ng, dn ti thng c im hay mt i quyn pht cu. Tuy nhin,trc khipht cu tt th bn phi bit lut v pht cu lng ng lut. Bi vit hm nay chng ta s cng tm hiu v<a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/luat-phat-cau-long-danh-doi.html\">lut pht cu lng nh i</a>cho ngi chi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>P</strong><strong>ht cu lng nh i trong thi u</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trong luyn tp cng nh thi u cu lng, th ng tc pht cu l hay b phm lut v mt li nht. Khng phi ch v nhng ngi chi phong tro mi thng phm lut v khng bit r nhng quy nh ca lut khi pht cu. M c nhng vn ng vin c ng cp i khi cng b trng ti bt pht khi pht cu.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Lut p</strong><strong>ht cu</strong><strong>lng nh i</strong></p>\r\n<p>Lut pht cu lngnh i l phn khc bit nht trong lut cu lng i v lut cu lng n.</p>\r\n<p> pht cu v  nhn cu:</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/luat-phat-cau-long-danh-doi-1.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p> Ngi chi bn pht cu s pht cu t  pht cu bn phi khi bn h cha ghi im hoc ghi c im chn trong vn .</p>\r\n<p> Ngi chi bn pht cu s pht cu t  pht cu bn tri khi h ghi c im l trong vn .</p>\r\n<p> Ngi chi c qu pht cu ln cui trc  ca bn pht cu s gi nguyn v tr ng m t   ngi chi ny  thc hin ln pht cu cui cho bn mnh v s p dng ngc li cho ng i ca ngi nhn cu.</p>\r\n<p> Ngi chi ca bn nhn cu ang ng trong  pht cu cho i din s l ngi nhn cu.</p>\r\n<p> Ngi chi s khng thay i v tr ng tng ng ca mnh cho n khi h thng mt im m bn ca h ang nm quyn pht cu.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xem thm</strong>:<a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/cach-giao-cau-long-dung-luat.html\">Cch giao cu lng ng lut</a>v sai lut bn nn bit.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/luat-phat-cau-long-danh-doi-2.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Ghi im v</strong><strong>pht</strong><strong>cu trong lut cu lng i</strong></p>\r\n<p> Nu bn pht cu thng pha cu, h s ghi cho mnh mt im. Ngi pht cu tip tc thc hin qu pht cu t  pht cu tng ng cn li.</p>\r\n<p> Nu bn nhn cu thng pha cu, h s ghi cho mnh mt im. Bn nhn cu lc ny tr thnh bn pht cu mi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Trnh t pht cu</strong><strong>trong lut pht cu lng nh i</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trong bt k vn no, quyn pht cu cng c chuyn tun t:</p>\r\n<p> T ngi pht cu u tin khi bt u vn u   pht cu bn phi n ng i ca ngi nhn cu u tin. Lc ny qu pht cu c thc hin t  pht cu bn tri sang ng i ca ngi pht cu u tin.</p>\r\n<p> n ngi nhn cu u tin v tr li ngi pht cu u tin, v c tip tc nh th.</p>\r\n<p> Khng ngi chi no c pht cu sai phin, nhn cu sai phin, hoc nhn hai qu pht cu lin tip trong cng mt vn u, ngoi tr cc trng hp nu  iu 12.</p>\r\n<p> Bt k ngi chi no ca bn thng vn cng c th pht cu u tin  vn tip theo, v bt k ngi chi no ca bn thua vn cng c th nhn cu u tin  vn tip theo.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/luat-phat-cau-long-danh-doi-3.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>{youtube}https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3fZWVJtsDIs{/youtube}</p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-12-13 08:36:43', 67, '', '2023-12-13 09:19:13', 67, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 08:36:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 2, 5, '', '', 1, 8, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(8, 99, 'HNG DN PHT CU TRONG NH N', 'hu-ng-d-n-phat-c-u-trong-danh-don', '<p>Pht cu l c nh u tin bt u pha cu. Nghe c v n gin nhng khi thi u thc t, thi im pht cu c th ni l kh nhy cm trong c nh i v nh n, c th quyt nh 60% kt qu thng thua ca pha cu. Vy pht cu nh th no  chim c u th so vi i th? Sau y hy cng tm hiu cch pht cu lng n ng lut v hiu qu nht.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2><strong>1. Kch thc sn theo lut cu lng n</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Theo lut cu lng n do Lin on Cu lng Quc t BWF quy nh, sn cu lng n c kch thc:<br />- Chiu di 13.4m<br />- Chiu rng: 5.18m<br />-  di ng cho: 14.3m<br />Ngoi ra cc quy nh v ng k bin, chiu cao li ging vi quy nh trong cu lng i.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/cach-phat-cau-long-don-co-ban-nhat-1.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h2><strong>2. Phm vi giao cu v nhn cu</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Theo lut cu lng n, phm vi giao v nhn cu trong nh n c gii hn bi ng trung tm, vch giao cu ngn, ng bin dc pha trong v vch giao cu di (cng chnh l ng bin ngang cui sn).<br />Mi phn sn s c chia lm 2 na tri phi. Khi giao hoc nhn cu, ngi chi s ng  1 trong 2 v tr na bn tri hoc na bn phi, ty thuc vo im s hin c ca ngi giao cu. Ngi nhn cu s ng  phn sn i din cho nhau so vi ngi giao cu. C 2 ngi chi khi giao nhn cu khng c ng chm ng bin.<br />Nu ngi giao cu c im s chn (0, 2, 4, 6, 8,...), h s thc hin giao cu  na phn sn bn phi trn sn ca mnh. Ngi nhn cu s thc hin nhn cu  na phn sn bn phi trn sn ca mnh.<br />Nu ngi giao cu c im s l (1, 3, 5, 7,...), h s thc hin giao cu  na phn sn bn tri trn sn ca mnh. Ngi nhn cu s thc hin nhn cu  na phn sn bn tri trn sn ca mnh.<br />Theo lut thi u cu lng n cng nh cu lng i, mt khi vt bt u chuyn ng v pha sau ngi giao cu, bt k tr hon no cho vic giao cu c xem l bt hp l. Khi giao cu, vt phi t thp hn hoc bng 1.15m tnh t mt sn tr ln. Khi nh cu, thn vt ca ngi giao cu phi lun hng xung di. Vt ca ngi giao cu phi chuyn ng lin tc t lc bt u giao cu cho n lc nh i. ng i ca cu s t di vt qua li v ri vo  ngi nhn cu.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/cach-phat-cau-long-don-co-ban-nhat-2.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h2><strong>3. Cch pht cu lng n hiu qu</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Sau khi nm c lut pht cu lng n, ngi chi cn c k thut v cch pht cu lng n ng  chim c u th so vi i th.</p>\r\n<p><em>a/ K thut pht cu thun tay</em><br />K thut giao cu thun tay thng c dng ch yu trong nh n. Cc bc thc hin ng tc nh sau:<br />- Bc 1: ng trc vch giao cu, chn pha tay cm vt t pha sau, mi bn chn hng sang ngang; chn cn li t pha trc, mi chn hng v pha trc. Hai chn dn u trng tm, khong cch gia hai chn rng gn bng vai.<br />- Bc 2: Tay phi cm vt nng ln, gi hi khuu, tay cm cu t ngang tht lng, mt quan st i phng.<br />- Bc 3: Dn trng tm sang chn sau, tay cm vt nng ln cao, tay cm cu nng ln ngang ngc.<br />- Bc 4: Tay cm vt vung vt t pha sau ln, tay cm cu th cu ri pha trc ngi, vung vt nh vo qu cu theo hng t pha sau nh ln.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/cach-phat-cau-long-don-co-ban-nhat-3.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>b/ K thut pht cu tri tay</em><br />K thut giao cu tri tay c th dng trong c nh i v nh n nhng thng c dng ch yu trong nh i. y l cch giao cu c dng ph bin. Cc bc thc hin ng tc nh sau:<br />- Bc 1: ng trc vch giao cu, mt hng v pha li. Chn pha tay cm vt ng trc, mi chn hng v pha trc; chn cn li t pha sau, mi chn hng v pha trc. Hai chn ng rng gn bng vai.<br />- Bc 2: Dn trng tm vo chn trc, thn ngi hi a v trc, khuu tay phi co li, dng cch cm vt tri tay v a vt ngang ra  v tr ngang hng. Mt vt  di cnh bn tri, ngn tr v ngn ci tay tri cm u lng qu cu   hng xung di t.<br />- Bc 3: Thn cu i din thng vi mt vt, cng tay ko theo c tay ct y ngang ra trc lm sao cho qu cu lng bay thnh mt ng vng cung.</p>\r\n<p><em>c/ Cc ng cu c bn khi thc hin pht cu</em><br />Ty vo chin thut ca ngi chi, c th pht cu theo 2 kiu l pht cu cao, su v pht cu thp, gn.<br />- Pht cu cao, su c ngha l nh qu cu bay ln cao v ri  khu vc cui sn i phng. Mc ch ca k thut pht cu cao, su l dn i phng v pha cui sn, to khong trng  khu vc pha gia sn v trn li. Pht cu cao, su thng dng trong nh n, p dng khi i phng c k thut di chuyn km, kh nng tn cng yu.<br />- Pht cu thp, gn c ngha l nh qu cu n v tr gc trn phn sn i phng, gn vch giao cu vi qu o gn st li. Pht cu thp, gn c th dng trong c nh i v nh n. Mc ch l  hn ch kh nng tn cng ca i phng, nu p dng ng k thut v chn im ri tt c th dn i phng vo th b ng, to c hi tn cng  lt cu tip theo.</p>\r\n<p>Nh vy mnh  hng dn cho cc bn cch pht cu lng n hiu qu nht. Hy vng bi vit ny s hu ch vi cc bn.</p>\r\n<p>{youtube}https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xRpojimCCjM{/youtube}</p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-12-13 08:38:34', 67, '', '2023-12-13 09:18:11', 67, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 08:38:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 4, 4, '', '', 1, 8, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(9, 100, '4 CCH PHT CU LNG HIU QU CN NM VNG', '4-cach-phat-c-u-long-hi-u-qu-c-n-n-m-v-ng', '<p><a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/cach-phat-cau-long.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cch pht cu lng</a>l mt trong nhng k thut quan trng bn cn nm vng, khng nhng nh hng n chin thut nh m cn nh hng trc tip n vic gip bn ch ng hay b ng so vi i th.</p>\r\n<p>Cch pht cu lng c chia thnh 4 loi,  l pht cu thun tay cao su, tri tay thp gn, cao tay v thp tay. Mi kiu s c t th v k thut pht khc nhau.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1. Cch pht cu lng thun tay cao su</strong></p>\r\n<p>1.1. T th chun b:</p>\r\n<p>Bc chn tri ln trc, mi chn tri hng v li, chn phi pha sau, mi chn phi hng v bn phi. Trng tm chia u  c hai chn, khong cch gia hai chn rng bng vai, th lng ngi, hi  v pha trc.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/cach-phat-cau-long-1.webp\" alt=\"cch pht cu lng\" width=\"300\" height=\"89\" /></p>\r\n<p>Vi cch pht cu lng thun tay cao su, trc khi pht cu, tay phi cm vt nng ln, gi hi khy, ngn ci v ngn tr ca tay tri cm cu t ngang tht lng, mt nhn i th  quan st.</p>\r\n<p>1.2 Gi vt</p>\r\n<p>Khi gi vt  chun b cho ng tc pht cu, thn ngi chuyn v bn phi, vai hng v li, trng tm chuyn sang chn phi, tay phi nng ln v tay tri cm cu a ngang ngc.</p>\r\n<p>1.3 Vung vt</p>\r\n<p>Khi tay phi cm vt a ln, tay tri bung cu, lc ny c gng dui c tay phi ra, ngn tay nm cht vt, cu tip xc vung gc vi mt vt  pht cu.</p>\r\n<p>1.4 Kt thc</p>\r\n<p>Sau khi pht cu thnh cng, tay cm vt s theo qun tnh hng v pha bn tri, nhanh chng thu vt v trc ngc v chy n v tr trung tm sn  chun b nh tr pha cu ca i phng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2. Cch pht cu lng tri tay thp gn</strong></p>\r\n<p>2.1 Chun b</p>\r\n<p>ng pha sau ng pht cu gn khong 10-50cm, gn ng trung tm (c khi  gn bin dc). Mt hng v li, hai bn chn ng theo t th trc sau (khng phn bit chn no ng trc).</p>\r\n<p>2.2 Gi vt</p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/cach-phat-cau-long-2.webp\" alt=\"cch pht cu lng\" width=\"300\" height=\"171\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Trng tm ri vo chn trc, thn hi lao v trc, khuu tay phi co li, dng cch cm vt tri tay v a vt ngang ra  khong ngang tht lng. Mt vt lc ny  di cnh bn tri, ngn ci v ngn tr tay tri gi chc 2-3 lng v cho  cu hng xung.</p>\r\n<p>2.3 Vung vt</p>\r\n<p>Trong cch pht cu lng tri tay thp gn, thn cu i din thng vi mt vt, cng tay ko theo c tay ct y ngang ra trc lm cho cu bay ng vng cung hn mp trn ca li v ri xung  khu vc gn  ng pht cu gn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xem thm:</strong><a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/:/shopvnb.com/ky-thuat-danh-cau-long-co-ban-ban-can-biet-dap-cau.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">K thut nh cu lng c bn bn cn bit: p cu</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>3. Cch pht cu lng cao tay</strong></p>\r\n<p>3.1 T th chun b</p>\r\n<p>ng tc gi vt hay vung vt tng t nh trong cch pht cu lng thun tay cao su. im khc nhau l khi tip xc gia vt vi cu, khng vung vt v pha trc vi lc ln nht m c ch sc li  cu bay nhanh v thp hn.</p>\r\n<p>3.2 u im ca cch pht cu lng cao tay</p>\r\n<p> vng ca pht cu cao tay thp hn pht cu cao xa  i th nhy ln nh c ng cu vng, im ri cng phi  st ng bin cui sn. Tc  cu bay trn khng nhanh hn cch pht cu lng cao su, y l kiu pht cu tn cng.</p>\r\n<p><strong>4. Cch pht cu lng thp tay</strong></p>\r\n<p>4.1 T th chun b</p>\r\n<p>Cc t th cng nh chun b ging vi cch pht cu tri tay thp gn, khc  thi im nh cu th ct bn pha sau  cu v c tay t cong xung nhanh chng thng ra vung ln pha trc  cu bt ng bay n ngi nhn.</p>\r\n<p>4.2 u im ca cch pht cu lng thp tay</p>\r\n<p>Ging nh pht cu va thun tay, tuy nhin mang li tnh bt ng v  uy hip cao hn cho i th so vi cch pht cu cao va.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-12-13 08:40:18', 67, '', '2023-12-13 08:40:18', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 08:40:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 3, '', '', 1, 2, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(10, 101, 'CCH P CU', 'cach-d-p-c-u', '<p>p cu l k thut c yu thch nht trong b mn cu lng. Hu nh ngi chi no d l chi lu nm hay va mi bt u lm quen cng u mong mun thnh thc ng tc p cu trc tin, bi n em li s phn khch khi ginh c im, ng thi k nng p cu cng phn no th hin c trnh  ca ngi chi. Sau y mnh xin gii thiu chi tit cho cc bn v k thut p cu, dnh cho cc bn mi bt u chi hay nhng bn cha c c c p cu hon ho nht.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2><strong>1. K thut p cu l g?</strong></h2>\r\n<p>p cu l mt k thut tn cng, ngi chi s thc hin mt c nh mnh t trn cao,  v tr cu cao nht, lm cho cu i nhanh v pha phn sn i phng vi tc  cng nhanh cng tt. p cu l k thut c xc sut ghi im nhiu nht, do  k thut p cu cng thun thc, tc  p cu cng nhanh th cng d ginh phn thng trc i th. K thut p cu bao gm p cu i chn ti ch, y l k thut p cu lng c bn, v k thut bt nhy p cu.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/lam-sao-de-dap-cau-manh-huong-dan-ky-thuat-dap-cau-chi-tiet-1.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h2><strong>2. Cch thc hin k thut p cu</strong></h2>\r\n<p>a/ T th chun b:<br />- Chun b trong t th i cu, hai chn ng dang rng, gi hi khuu, tay cn vt gi cao ngang trc mt.<br />- H thp tm mt  ngang mt li, mt di theo cu.</p>\r\n<p>b/ Chuyn ng ca vt v c th<br />- Khi i phng nh cu sang cao pha trn u th lp tc xoay ngi sang pha tay cm vt (tay thun), trng tm chuyn sang chn pha tay cm vt.<br />- Tay cm vt a ra sau, u vt hng ln cao. Tay cn li gi cao trc mt.<br />- Vai bn tay thun h thp v pha sau, vai kia nng cao hng v pha cu.<br />- T th un cng v pha trc hnh cnh cung. Sau  p mnh chn pha sau, kt hp xoay hng, lng, vai, tay cm vt vung ln cao ra pha trc. Mt vt tip xc vung gc vi ng cu.<br />- im tip xc cu  v tr cao nht c th, chch trc trn cch trn khong 80-90cm. Trong qu trnh thc hin k thut p cu cn kt hp gp thn ngi v gp c tay  cu i cm hn.</p>\r\n<p>c/ Kt thc ng tc<br />- Vt theo  a t trn xung di, thn ngi theo  tin v pha trc, chn pha tay cm vt bc ln trc  gi thng bng.<br />- Nhanh chng quay tr li t th chun b, hai chn dang rng, gi hi khuu, vt gi cao ngang tm mt chun b cho pha cu tip theo.</p>\r\n<p>Trn y l k thut p cu lng c bn,  tng sc tn cng cho k thut p cu, c th kt hp ng tc bt nhy  tip xc cu  v tr cao hn, cho pha p cu cm hn.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>3. Nhng li sai thng gp khi thc hin k thut p cu</strong></h2>\r\n<p>- Khng chun b t th sn sng. Trong mi tnh hung ngi chi cn c th th chun b sn sng cho mi pha cu, iu ny gip cho ngi chi ch ng hn trong cc pha cu, khi b ri vo th b ng hoc khng bt kp cu.<br />- Cm vt qu cht hoc qu lng.  thc hin k thut p cu lng ng cch, ngi chi cn th lng tay cm vt trong sut qu trnh thc hin ng tc, ch khi mt vt tip xc vi cu mi nm cht tay cm vt, to lc bc pht gip cho pha p cu c tc  nhanh nht.<br />- B qua ng tc ca tay khng cm vt. Khi thc hin k thut p cu, tay khng cm vt gi cao trc mt c tc dng nh hng qu cu trong khng gian, gip ngi chi nh vo qu cu  v tr chnh xc nht, ng thi gi cn bng cho c th.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/lam-sao-de-dap-cau-manh-huong-dan-ky-thuat-dap-cau-chi-tiet-2.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>- Tip xc cu cha ng v tr. Vi ngi mi chi cha xc nh ng im ri ca qu cu, dn n tip xc cu  v tr qu gn hoc qu xa. Ngoi ra ngi chi cn c k thut di chuyn hp l v nhanh chng n v tr cu ri  nh trng cu  t th thun li nht.<br />- Cch vung vt cha ng. Trong k thut p cu ngi chi cn kt hp cng lc cc c hng, lng, vai, cnh tay v c tay. T lc xoay hng n lc vung vt cn thc hin mt cch tun t  vn dng lc tt nht.<br />- p cu xong khng tr li v tr chun b. Sau khi p cu nhiu ngi chi c thi quen quan st ng cu bay mt lc ri mi bt u di chuyn, iu ny khin cho tc  x l pha cu tip theo b chm li, to ra s h trn sn dn n mt im.</p>\r\n<p>Nh vy mnh  chia s vi cc bn chi tit v ng tc cng nh l nhng li sai thng gp trong k thut p cu. Cn phi lu  rng y l mt k thut tng i kh, i vi nhng bn mi bt u chi khng nn nn nng hc cch p cu m hy dnh thi gian tp luyn cc k thut c bn trc, c bit l hc cch di chuyn sao cho hp l v linh hot nht. Nh vy vi to c nn tng tt  tp luyn nhng k thut nng cao hn.</p>\r\n<p>{youtube}https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CW5zLvryQ-4&amp;t=1s{/youtube}</p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-12-13 08:41:27', 67, '', '2023-12-13 09:17:23', 67, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 08:41:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 5, 2, '', '', 1, 8, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(11, 102, 'T TH NH CU CHUN', 'tu-th-danh-c-u-chu-n', '<p>T th anh cu lng ng v chun giup ngi chi cu lng thc hin tt nhng ky thut, nhm at  chinh xac va sc manh trong qua trinh luyn tp cung nh thi u. Vi mt t th anh cu tt ngi chi se hoan thin tng ky thut cu lng c ban va nng cao. Bai vit hm nay chung ta se cung tim hiu v t th chun b trong cu lng hiu qua cho ngi chi.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>1. T th anh cu lng thp</strong></h2>\r\n<p> y cng l t th phng th trong cu lng: Hai chn ng song song trn na trc bn chn, khong cch gia hai chn rng bng vai, gi hi khuu. Trng lng c th dn u ln hai chn, lng cong t nhin, u nga, tay thun cm vt, mt vt  pha trc thn ngi ngang vi tm bng.</p>\r\n<p> Tay kia th lng t nhin, t th anh cu lng nay ny thng sdng trong tp luyn hoc khi phng th trong thi u.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>2. T th anh cu lng cao</strong></h2>\r\n<p> Chn khng cng bn vi tay cm vt  pha trc, chn cng bn vi tay cm vt  pha sau,ng trn na trc bn chn. Khong cch gia hai chn rng bng vai.</p>\r\n<p> Trng lng c th dn vo chn trc hi khuu lng cong t nhin. Tay thun cm vt, mt vt cao ngang trn.</p>\r\n<p> Tay con lai th lng t nhin, t th anh cu lngny thng s dng trong thi u cu lng, khi chun b  pht cuhoc khi s dng cc k thut nh cu cao tay.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><strong>Xem thm</strong>:<a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/cach-cam-vot-cau-long-trai-tay.html\">Cch cm vt cu lng tri tay</a>ung ky thut.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>3. T th chun b trong cu lng khi thc hin mt s ky thut cn ban</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Trong tng ky thut anh cu lng cn ban se oi hoi ngi chi vi nhng t th anh cu lng khac nhau:</p>\r\n<h3><strong>T th nh cu lng khipht cu thun tay</strong></h3>\r\n<p> Chn trai trc, mui ban chn trai hng v phia li, chn phai sau, mui chn phai hng xoay v bn phai, khoang cach gia hai chn gn rng bng vai, trong tm u trn hai chn, ngi ng t nhin tha long, hi  v trc.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h3><strong>T th cu lng khipht cu lng tri tay thp gn</strong></h3>\r\n<p> V tr pht cu c th  pha sau ng pht cu gn khong 10  50 cm v gn vi ng trung tm. Cng c khi  sau vch pht cu gn v gn ng bin dc. Ngi pht cu ng mt hng v li. V tr hai bn chn ng tch trc sau (chn tri hoc chn phi  trc u c th c).</p>\r\n<p> T th nh cu lng khi pht cu: Thn ngi hi lao v trc, trng tm c th ri vo chn trc, tay phi co khuu, s dng cch cm vt tri tay v a vt ngang ra  khong ngang tht lng, mt vt  di cnh bn tri c th.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>T th cu lng khi  phat cu trong anh n</strong></h3>\r\n<p> T th ng th chn tri  trc chn phi  sau, hai gi hi khuu, hp bng v ngc, trng tm c th ri vo chn trc, gt ca bn chn sau hi king, mt bn ca thn ngi hng v li, vt a v trc thn, hai mt nhn chm ch vo i phng.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/tu-the-danh-cau-long-1.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h3><strong>T th nh cu lng khi  phat cu trong anh i</strong></h3>\r\n<p> ng  t th chun b c bn ging vi t th chun b  giao cu ca nh n, ch c im hi khc l thn ngi ng ra trc ln hn, trng tm c th c th ty  mun t ln chn no cng c, vt c th gi ln hi cao mt cht.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>T th bc nhay p cu</strong></h3>\r\n<p>  thc hin t th nh cu lng ny, u tin thchin ng tc nghing ngi, chn phi li sau mt bc chun b bt nhy. Sau khi bt nhy a thn ngi ln cao  pha sau bn phi, thn trn nga ra sau  pha bn phi hoc thnh t th cnh cung ngc, tay phi nng ln pha trn bn phi, vai ko ra sau ht mc.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>T th phng th trong cu lng</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Hai chn ng song song trn na trc bn chn, khong cch gia hai chn rng bng vai, gi hi khuu. Trng lng c th dn u ln hai chn, lng cong t nhin, u nga, tay thun cm vt, mt vt  pha trc thn ngi ngang vi tm bng.</p>', '', 1, 2, '2023-12-13 08:44:39', 67, '', '2023-12-13 08:44:39', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 08:44:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 1, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(12, 103, ' Giy Lining c tt, c bn khng & nhng sn phm ni bt', 'giay-lining-co-t-t-co-b-n-khong-nh-ng-s-n-ph-m-n-i-b-t', '<h2>Xut x ca thng hiu Lining</h2>\r\n<p>Lining l mt trong nhng thng hiu danh ting ni ln t Trung Quc, l cng ty chuyn v giy dp, trang phc v cc ph kin th thao. Vi kinh nghim sn xut, cng b dy lch s cng nh s tin phong trong nhng phong cch mi, Lining  vt ra khi th trng ni a Trung Quc, v cnh tranh trc tip vi cc hng Nike, Adidas, Re-book</p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_1305\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1305 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Xut x ca thng hiu Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-x%E1%BB%A9-c%E1%BB%A7a-th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-hi%E1%BB%87u-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Xut x ca thng hiu Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Xut-x-ca-thng-hiu-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" />\r\n<figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-1305\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Xut x ca thng hiu Lining</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Nm 1990, tp on sn xut dng c th thao Lining Sport c Lining  vn ng vin th dc Olympic thnh lp. Nm 1982 ng dnh c 7 trong s 8 huy chng vng trong hng mc dnh cho nam ti Cp th dc th gii ln th 6, v tr thnh biu tng th thao  Trung Quc. Sau khi gii ngh, ng  chuyn nim am m dnh cho th thao sang vic gy dng mt cng ty dng c th thao chuyn nghip.</p>\r\n<p>Sau gn 20 nm, n nay Lining  ni ln nh mt trong thng hiu y ha hn ca th trng Trung Quc. C nhng  kin cho rng, mt trong nhng yu t thnh cng ca Lining  th trng Trung Quc chnh l sc cun ht v tnh biu tng ca nh sng lp Lining, cng nh vic cng ty  tn dng cc s kin th thao n mc ti a, cho d gi y ng  tr nn hi c knh i vi nhng khch hng tr tui. Bn ngh sao v iu ny?</p>\r\n<p>Nhng thnh cng m Lining t c da trn 4 yu t chnh  l sc cun ht v s ni ting ca c nhn Lining, mng li phn phi mnh m  th trng Trung Quc, vai tr nh ti tr cho mt s s kin th thao ni ting v mc gi hp dn ca mi sn phm. Lining sn xut nhng sn phm c cht lng ngang hng vi sn phm ca Nike, nhng li s hu mc gi bng na tm ca Nike m thi, chng ta s tm hiu chi tit hn v vn  ny  di.</p>\r\n<p>Lining  ln sn sang th trng tiu th  Vit Nam v t c nhng thnh tu ng m c. Lining hin ang l mt trong nhng thng hiu c ngi tiu dng kh a chung v lun u tin l mt trong nhng s la chn hng u ca ngi tiu dng Vit Nam.</p>\r\n<p>Vi mt xut x cng s pht trin tm c nh vy, chc hn bn cng  phn no on c cu tr li cho vn  giy Lining c tt khng c phi khng? Vn  ny s c minh chng r nt hn na thng qua phn phn khc gi thnh sn phm m chng ta s tm hiu ngay by gi.</p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Phan_khuc_gia_thanh_san_pham_cua_thuong_hieu_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Phn khc gi thnh sn phm ca thng hiu Lining</h2>\r\n<p>Ling cng ging nh nhng thng hiu sn xut giy khc, c nhng dng sn phm vi nhng phn khc gi thnh khc nhau. Mi phn khc gi sn phm ca Lining u s hu mt c im c trng ring v chng ta s tm hiu k hn v tng phn khc,  gip bn c th hiu su sc hn v thng hiu Lining ny cng nh phn no xc nh giy Lining c tt khng nh!</p>\r\n<p> phn khc gi tm r, bn cng c th la chn c cho mnh mt i giy bn b, chc chn v c  bn thch thc vi thi gian. Nhng sn phm  phn khc ny thng c thit k ngoi hnh kh n gin, nhng khng h km phn sang chnh, n tng. c bit l vic s dng cc sn phm ny cng khin bn  mt thi gian trong vic la chn trang phc, v a phn nhng sn phm ny u kh n gin nn rt d phi .</p>\r\n<p> phn khc gi tm trung, bn cng s tm c nhng sn phm tng t nh nhng sn phm thuc phn khc gi tm r, nhng nhng dng sn phm ny c tp trung vo chi tit hn. iu ny gp phn lm gia tng thm phong cch cho ngi s dng, gip h tr nn n tng v ni bt hn khi mang nhng i giy Lining trn i chn ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Lining khng ging nh nhng thng hiu khc, v khng qu tp trung vo nhng sn phm thuc phn khc gi tm cao cp. Nhng sn phm thuc phn khc ny c thit k t m, cng phu n tng chi tit, nhm em li cho ngi dng cm nhn v mt sn phm hon ho v n tng n tng chi tit. Nhng sn phm ca phn khc ny ch yu hng n phc v cc khch hng tim nng yu thch v p phong cch ca hng ny m thi.</p>\r\n<p>Vi nhng thng tin trn, chc hn bn  hiu hn v vn  giy Lining c tt khng ri nh? c mt iu chc chn l d bn l ai? Lm cng vic g? C s thch ra sao? V s hu mc lng th no? Th bn cng c th d dng tm c cho mnh mt i giy ng   Lining.</p>\r\n<p> c th chng minh cho iu va khng nh, mi bn hy cng vi chng ti i tm hiu v mt s nhng dng sn phm ni ting ca Lining ang rt hot trn th trng hin nay nh!</p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Mot_so_dong_san_pham_noi_tieng_cua_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Mt s dng sn phm ni ting ca Lining</h2>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_tap_luyen_the_thao_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy tp luyn th thao Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Nhc n nhng dng sn phm ni bt ca Lining, giy tp luyn th thao ca nam v n l dng sn phm ni bt m chng ta khng th no b qua. V vn  giy tp luyn th thao ca giy Lining c tt khng cng l mt trong nhng vn  m ngi tiu dng rt quan tm.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1303 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy tp luyn th thao Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-t%E1%BA%ADp-luy%E1%BB%87n-th%E1%BB%83-thao-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy tp luyn th thao Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-tp-luyn-th-thao-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Nhng i giy dng ny c thit k a dng v mu m cng nh mu sc. c bit chng c thit k ph hp vi nhng cht liu tt nht, gip cho ngi dng c th s dng trong sut mt thi gian di khi tp luyn cc b mn th thao m khng cm thy au chn.</p>\r\n<p>Mt chi tit m chng ta khng th b qua  l gi thnh ca dng giy tp luyn ny. Mc d c thit k a dng v cht lng nh vy, nhng trn thc t nhng i giy ny li s hu mc gi tm r v tm trung l ch yu. Nu nh bn c yu cu cao hn na v cht lng cng nh phong cch th bn cng c th tm thy dng giy tp luyn  mc gi tm cao cp bn nh!</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_chay_bo_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy chy b Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Nu bn thc mc giy chy b ca giy Lining c tt khng? Th chngt i sn sng tr li cho bn l c. Giy ny c thit k c bit nn ph hp cho b mn th thao chy b, khin ngi dng cm nhn c s thoi mi trong mt thi gian di khi s dng sn phm. Bn cng c th d dng bt gp hnh nh quen thuc ca nhng i giy chy b ny trong mt s cuc thi chy mang tm c quc t.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1306 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy chy b Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-ch%E1%BA%A1y-b%E1%BB%99-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy chy b Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-chy-b-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Vy c l do no khin cho ngi tiu dng li tin tng v la chn dng sn phm ny n vy?  chnh l cht lng tuyt vi m n em li cho ngi s dng, cng thm vi mc gi tm trung m chng s hu.  chnh l nhng yu t khin cho dng sn phm giy chy b Lining lun c ngi tiu dng ng h ht sc nhit tnh.</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_thoi_trang_the_thao_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy thi trang th thao Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Giy thi trang th thao Lining l dng sn phm c ngi tiu dng cc k a chung trong thi gian gn y. Nhng sn phm dng ny c ch trng nhiu hn n phong cch, chnh v vy dng sn phm ny cc k ph hp vi nhng ai a chung phong cch thi trang v c tnh ni bt.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1304 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-th%E1%BB%9Di-trang-th%E1%BB%83-thao-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-thi-trang-th-thao-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Mc d l dng giy ch trng n yu t thi trang, nhng khng phi v vy m Lining khng tp trung n cht lng ca dng sn phm hot hit ny. Trong mi trng hp, bn hy nh rng chnh cht lng ca sn phm  gp phn quan trng to nn mt thng hiu Lining ni ting nh ngy hm nay. Nu bn am m phong cch thi trang n tng v c tnh, th ng nn b qua dng sn phm giy thi trang th thao Lining ni ting ny nh!</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_bong_ro_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy bng r Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Ngoi nhng dng sn phm trn, dng giy bng r Lining cng l mt trong nhng dng sn phm c ngi tiu dng kh a chung trong thi gian gn y. Rt kh c th tm c cho bn mt i giy c thit k dnh ring cho b mn th thao bng r vi cht lng cc nh m li s hu mt mc gi v cng  hi nh  Lining y nh!</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1304 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-th%E1%BB%9Di-trang-th%E1%BB%83-thao-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-thi-trang-th-thao-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Vi cu hi giy bng r ca giy Lining c tt khng? Chng ti xin khng nh l c. Thit k giy a dng v mu m cng nh mu sc, s dng nhng cht liu hng u trong lnh vc sn xut giy v thit k tinh t da theo nhng yu cu ca b mn bng r. Bn c th s dng dng giy bng r ny trong qu trnh tp luyn cng nh thi u trong sut thi gian di m khng lo au chn ri.</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_cau_long_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy cu lng Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Giy cu lng Lining cng l mt trong nhng dng giy chng ta khng nn b qua. Nu bn l mt ngi am m b mn th thao cu lng, th hy tu ngay mt i giy cu lng Lining vo t giy ca mnh nh! Thit k tinh t, a dng v thch hp vi nhng yu cu ca b mn th thao chc chn s lm bn hi lng khi s dng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1302 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy cu lng Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-c%E1%BA%A7u-l%C3%B4ng-Lining.jpeg\" alt=\"Giy cu lng Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"667\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-cu-lng-Lining.jpeg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Nhng i giy dng ny ch trng nhiu n cht lng, nhm em li cho ngi dng cm gic thoi mi nht c th khi s dng sn phm trong sut mt thi gian di, khi tp luyn hay thi u b mn cu lng. V gi c m dng sn phm ny s hu cng l nhng con s tm thp v tm trung m thi. Vy nn vic s hu mt i giy dng ny cng khng phi l vn  qu kh khn u bn nh!</p>', '', -2, 2, '2023-12-13 09:01:16', 67, '', '2023-12-13 09:01:16', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 09:01:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 0, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', '');
