hc, c nhng dng sn phm vi nhng phn khc gi thnh khc nhau. Mi phn khc gi sn phm ca Lining u s hu mt c im c trng ring v chng ta s tm hiu k hn v tng phn khc,  gip bn c th hiu su sc hn v thng hiu Lining ny cng nh phn no xc nh giy Lining c tt khng nh!</p>\r\n<p> phn khc gi tm r, bn cng c th la chn c cho mnh mt i giy bn b, chc chn v c  bn thch thc vi thi gian. Nhng sn phm  phn khc ny thng c thit k ngoi hnh kh n gin, nhng khng h km phn sang chnh, n tng. c bit l vic s dng cc sn phm ny cng khin bn  mt thi gian trong vic la chn trang phc, v a phn nhng sn phm ny u kh n gin nn rt d phi .</p>\r\n<p> phn khc gi tm trung, bn cng s tm c nhng sn phm tng t nh nhng sn phm thuc phn khc gi tm r, nhng nhng dng sn phm ny c tp trung vo chi tit hn. iu ny gp phn lm gia tng thm phong cch cho ngi s dng, gip h tr nn n tng v ni bt hn khi mang nhng i giy Lining trn i chn ca mnh.</p>\r\n<p>Lining khng ging nh nhng thng hiu khc, v khng qu tp trung vo nhng sn phm thuc phn khc gi tm cao cp. Nhng sn phm thuc phn khc ny c thit k t m, cng phu n tng chi tit, nhm em li cho ngi dng cm nhn v mt sn phm hon ho v n tng n tng chi tit. Nhng sn phm ca phn khc ny ch yu hng n phc v cc khch hng tim nng yu thch v p phong cch ca hng ny m thi.</p>\r\n<p>Vi nhng thng tin trn, chc hn bn  hiu hn v vn  giy Lining c tt khng ri nh? c mt iu chc chn l d bn l ai? Lm cng vic g? C s thch ra sao? V s hu mc lng th no? Th bn cng c th d dng tm c cho mnh mt i giy ng   Lining.</p>\r\n<p> c th chng minh cho iu va khng nh, mi bn hy cng vi chng ti i tm hiu v mt s nhng dng sn phm ni ting ca Lining ang rt hot trn th trng hin nay nh!</p>\r\n<h2><span id=\"Mot_so_dong_san_pham_noi_tieng_cua_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Mt s dng sn phm ni ting ca Lining</h2>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_tap_luyen_the_thao_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy tp luyn th thao Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Nhc n nhng dng sn phm ni bt ca Lining, giy tp luyn th thao ca nam v n l dng sn phm ni bt m chng ta khng th no b qua. V vn  giy tp luyn th thao ca giy Lining c tt khng cng l mt trong nhng vn  m ngi tiu dng rt quan tm.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1303 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy tp luyn th thao Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-t%E1%BA%ADp-luy%E1%BB%87n-th%E1%BB%83-thao-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy tp luyn th thao Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-tp-luyn-th-thao-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Nhng i giy dng ny c thit k a dng v mu m cng nh mu sc. c bit chng c thit k ph hp vi nhng cht liu tt nht, gip cho ngi dng c th s dng trong sut mt thi gian di khi tp luyn cc b mn th thao m khng cm thy au chn.</p>\r\n<p>Mt chi tit m chng ta khng th b qua  l gi thnh ca dng giy tp luyn ny. Mc d c thit k a dng v cht lng nh vy, nhng trn thc t nhng i giy ny li s hu mc gi tm r v tm trung l ch yu. Nu nh bn c yu cu cao hn na v cht lng cng nh phong cch th bn cng c th tm thy dng giy tp luyn  mc gi tm cao cp bn nh!</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_chay_bo_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy chy b Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Nu bn thc mc giy chy b ca giy Lining c tt khng? Th chngt i sn sng tr li cho bn l c. Giy ny c thit k c bit nn ph hp cho b mn th thao chy b, khin ngi dng cm nhn c s thoi mi trong mt thi gian di khi s dng sn phm. Bn cng c th d dng bt gp hnh nh quen thuc ca nhng i giy chy b ny trong mt s cuc thi chy mang tm c quc t.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1306 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy chy b Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-ch%E1%BA%A1y-b%E1%BB%99-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy chy b Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-chy-b-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Vy c l do no khin cho ngi tiu dng li tin tng v la chn dng sn phm ny n vy?  chnh l cht lng tuyt vi m n em li cho ngi s dng, cng thm vi mc gi tm trung m chng s hu.  chnh l nhng yu t khin cho dng sn phm giy chy b Lining lun c ngi tiu dng ng h ht sc nhit tnh.</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_thoi_trang_the_thao_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy thi trang th thao Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Giy thi trang th thao Lining l dng sn phm c ngi tiu dng cc k a chung trong thi gian gn y. Nhng sn phm dng ny c ch trng nhiu hn n phong cch, chnh v vy dng sn phm ny cc k ph hp vi nhng ai a chung phong cch thi trang v c tnh ni bt.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1304 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-th%E1%BB%9Di-trang-th%E1%BB%83-thao-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-thi-trang-th-thao-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Mc d l dng giy ch trng n yu t thi trang, nhng khng phi v vy m Lining khng tp trung n cht lng ca dng sn phm hot hit ny. Trong mi trng hp, bn hy nh rng chnh cht lng ca sn phm  gp phn quan trng to nn mt thng hiu Lining ni ting nh ngy hm nay. Nu bn am m phong cch thi trang n tng v c tnh, th ng nn b qua dng sn phm giy thi trang th thao Lining ni ting ny nh!</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_bong_ro_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy bng r Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Ngoi nhng dng sn phm trn, dng giy bng r Lining cng l mt trong nhng dng sn phm c ngi tiu dng kh a chung trong thi gian gn y. Rt kh c th tm c cho bn mt i giy c thit k dnh ring cho b mn th thao bng r vi cht lng cc nh m li s hu mt mc gi v cng  hi nh  Lining y nh!</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1304 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-th%E1%BB%9Di-trang-th%E1%BB%83-thao-Lining.jpg\" alt=\"Giy thi trang th thao Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-thi-trang-th-thao-Lining.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Vi cu hi giy bng r ca giy Lining c tt khng? Chng ti xin khng nh l c. Thit k giy a dng v mu m cng nh mu sc, s dng nhng cht liu hng u trong lnh vc sn xut giy v thit k tinh t da theo nhng yu cu ca b mn bng r. Bn c th s dng dng giy bng r ny trong qu trnh tp luyn cng nh thi u trong sut thi gian di m khng lo au chn ri.</p>\r\n<h3><span id=\"Giay_cau_long_Lining\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"></span>Giy cu lng Lining</h3>\r\n<p>Giy cu lng Lining cng l mt trong nhng dng giy chng ta khng nn b qua. Nu bn l mt ngi am m b mn th thao cu lng, th hy tu ngay mt i giy cu lng Lining vo t giy ca mnh nh! Thit k tinh t, a dng v thch hp vi nhng yu cu ca b mn th thao chc chn s lm bn hi lng khi s dng sn phm.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1302 entered lazyloaded\" title=\"fil Giy cu lng Lining\" src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Gi%C3%A0y-c%E1%BA%A7u-l%C3%B4ng-Lining.jpeg\" alt=\"Giy cu lng Lining\" width=\"600\" height=\"667\" data-lazy-src=\"https://foot.vn/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Giy-cu-lng-Lining.jpeg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" /></p>\r\n<p>Nhng i giy dng ny ch trng nhiu n cht lng, nhm em li cho ngi dng cm gic thoi mi nht c th khi s dng sn phm trong sut mt thi gian di, khi tp luyn hay thi u b mn cu lng. V gi c m dng sn phm ny s hu cng l nhng con s tm thp v tm trung m thi. Vy nn vic s hu mt i giy dng ny cng khng phi l vn  qu kh khn u bn nh!</p>', '', 1, 8, '2023-12-13 09:26:56', 67, '', '2023-12-13 09:27:41', 67, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 09:26:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 3, 2, '', '', 1, 2, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(14, 106, 'Kch thc sn cu lng tiu chun quc t cho nh n v nh i', 'kich-thu-c-san-c-u-long-tieu-chu-n-qu-c-t-cho-danh-don-va-danh-doi', '<p>Sn cu lng di bao nhiu mt? cch v sn cu lng cng nh<strong>kch thc sn cu lng</strong>tiu chun l nhng cu hi c rt nhiu ngi chi tm kim. Chng ra cng tm hiu k hn nh ! Kch thc tiu chunsn cu lngc quy nh bi Lin on Cu lng Th gii BWF. V quy nh chialoi hnh thi u m sn cu lng cng c hai loi  l: sn cu lng nh n v sn cu lng nh i. Cng shopvnb tm hiu v<a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/kich-thuoc-tieu-chuan-san-cau-long-va-dac-diem-san-cau-long.html\">kch thc sn cu lng</a>tiu chun,quy cch sn cu lng trong c nh n v nh i.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h2><strong>1. Kch thc sn cu lngtiu chun</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Khng phi ai cng bit kch thc tiu chun sn cu lng n v i theo quy nh quc t l bao nhiu. Kch thc sn cu lng c thit k dng hnh ch nht vi cc kch thcnh sau: Chiu di: 13.4m v chiu rng: 5.18m i vi sn nh n hoc 6.1m i vi sn nh i.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>1.1. Kch thc sn cu lng n</strong><strong></strong></h3>\r\n<p>Lin on Cu lng Th gii (BWF)quy nhkch thc sn cu lng nh n nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>- Chiu di: 13.4m</p>\r\n<p>- Chiu rng (khng tnh 2 ng bn): 5.18m</p>\r\n<p>-  di ng cho : 14.3m</p>\r\n<h3><strong>1.2. Kch thc sn cu lng i</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Lin on Cu lng Th gii (BWF)quy nh kch thc sn cu lng nh i nh sau:</p>\r\n<p>- Chiu di : 13.4m</p>\r\n<p>- Chiu rng,( tnh 2 ng bn) : 6.1m</p>\r\n<p>-  di ng cho : 14,3m</p>\r\n<h3><strong>1.3. Lu  vkch thc sn cu lngtiu chun</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Thng thng  phn bit vi nn th ng k bin s c mu vng hoc mu trng v cng c k bin c  dy khong 4cm. Ngoi ra, kch thc tiu chun sn cu lng n hay i cng tnh t mp ngoi cng bin ny n mp ngoi cng bin kia.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.shopvnb.com/uploads/images/tin_tuc/kich-thuoc-tieu-chuan-san-cau-long-va-dac-diem-san-cau-long-1.webp\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h3><strong>1.4 Din tch sn cu lng tiu chun</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Din tch sn cu lng lloi sn hnh ch nht vi kch thc vi nhng kch thc nh sau :</p>\r\n<p>-Chiu di : 13.4m</p>\r\n<p>-Chiu rng : nh n 5.18m v nh i 6.1m</p>\r\n<p>Ty vo kch thc tiu chunsn cu lng n hay i m chng ta c din tch khc nhau. C th sn cu lng n s c din tch 69,412m2 trong khi sn cu lng i c din tch 81,74m2.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>2. V sn cu lng p ng kch thc sn cu lng tiu chun quc t</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Da theo cc kch thc sn cu lng tiu chun, bn hon ton c th t v sn cu lng c cc vch k cng nh ng bin. Ch cn chun b vi dng c n gin v mt khong sn trng l bn cng c th t to c mt sn cu lng c kch thc chun. Tham kho hng dn chi tit cch v sn cu lng di y ca chng ti nh! Bao gm cv sn cu lng n v i.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Xem thm</strong>:<a href=\"https://shopvnb.com/cach-ve-san-cau-long.html\">Cch v sn cu lng ng kch thc tiu chun quc t</a>.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>3. Quy nh trang thit b ng kch thc sn cu lng tiu chun</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Ngoi nhng tiu chun v kch thc mt sn, din tch sn cu lng v khng gian xung quanh sn thi mt sn cu lng t chun quc t cn phi m bo cc quy nh v ph kin trong sn nh sau:</p>\r\n<h3><strong>3.1. Ct cng li sn cu lng</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Hai ct cng li phi c t ngay trn ng bin i  phc v cho nh cu lng n v nh cu lng i.</p>\r\n<p>Ct cu lng c chia ra lm 2 loi l:</p>\r\n<p>- Ct cu lng c bnh xe thun tin cho vic di chuyn v d dng tho lp.</p>\r\n<p>- Ct cu lng xp a nng dnh cho sn tp luyn hoc thi u cu lng chuyn nghip.</p>\r\n<p>Hai ct li c chiu cao tiu chun tnh t mt sn l 1m55. Hai ct cng li phi m bo chc chn, ng thng khi cng li ln.</p>\r\n<p>Hai ct tr cu lng cng nh cc ph kin i km (v d nh gh cu lng) khng c t vo trong sn m t  ngoi ng bin ca sn.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>3.2. Li cu lng</strong></h3>\r\n<p>- Li cu lng tiu chun c chiu rng 0.76m v chiu di ngang sn l 6.7m.</p>\r\n<p>- Li phi c lm bng nhng si nilon hoc si tng hp mm, c  dy u nhau v mu m. Mt li khng ln hn 20mm v khng nh hn 15mm.</p>\r\n<p>- Phn nh li s c cp bng np trng nm ph i ln dy li hoc dy cp chy xuyn qua np. Np li phi nm ph ln dy li hoc dy cp li.</p>\r\n<p>- Lut cu lng quc t cng quy nh, khng c  khong trng gia li v hai ct li. V tr li phi c kt st vo thn tr cu lng.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>3.3 Chiu cao mi che sn cu lng</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Chiu cao mi che cho sn cu lng theo tiu chun l 9m. Tuy nhin, hin nay c 1 s sn cu do quy nh khu vc khng cho xy dng qu cao. Cng nh nhiu anh em thu li kho bi  c sn  xy dng sn nn c nhiu sn cu ch tm 7-8m.</p>\r\n<h2><strong>3.4 Mt s ng k ng kch thc sn cu lng tiu chun</strong></h2>\r\n<p>Lin on cu lng Quc t quy nh, sn cu lng tiu chun s cha cc ng k chun dnh cho c ngi chi n v chi i. Trong :</p>\r\n<p>- Sn cu lng nh i c ch nh bi cc ng k bn ngoi.</p>\r\n<p>- Sn cu lng nh n s dng ng k bn trong.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Baseline</strong>: ng bin song song vi li v nm  cui mi bn sn.Chiu di ca Baselinebngchiu rng sn cu lng</p>\r\n<p><strong>Doubles sideline</strong>: L thng vi Baseline to ra cc ng ranh gii bn ngoi sn cu lng</p>\r\n<p><strong>Center line</strong>:ng k vung gc vi li, gip chia sn thnh 2 phn phi v tri  cc tuyn th thc hin giao cu</p>\r\n<p><strong>Short service line</strong>:Cch li khong 2m, cn c gi l vch giao cu ngn.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Long service line</strong>: y l vch giao cu di, khi giao cu bn khng c  cu i qu vch ny nh.</p>', '', 1, 8, '2023-12-13 09:28:59', 67, '', '2023-12-13 09:29:46', 67, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 09:28:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 2, 1, '', '', 1, 1, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', ''),
(15, 107, 'Li ch ca vic tp th thao mn Cu lng', 'l-i-ich-c-a-vi-c-t-p-th-thao-mon-c-u-long', '<p>Ai cng u c c m. D bn l ai? Lm g?  u th cng nn chi mt mn th thao no   c sc khe. V khi c sc khe th mi theo ui c c m. Vi ti ti chn mn Cu lng. No hy cng ti tm hiu v li ch ca mn th thao ny cc bn nh!</p>\r\n<p>Cu lng l mn th thao ph bin nht  Vit Nam ni chung v tnh Lng Sn ni ring, thng chi nh mt hot ng ngoi tri bnh thng trong sn hoc trn bi bin; Cc tr chi chnh thc c chi trn mt sn hnh ch nht. Tr chi  c pht trin gia ngi Anh n, v sau  lan rng khp th gii. Cu lng cng nm trong danh sch cnh tranh chnh thc ca Olympic, Seagames, Asian Games,  Chi cu lng c mt s li ch nht nh. Trc ht, n ci thin sc bn v s nhanh nhy ca ngi chi. Bn cnh , th dc th thao lun c li cho sc kho, v vy cu lng gip bn xy dng c bp, tng cng h min dch v h xng  Hn na, ng vai tr gii tr, n gip bn gii phng stress, trm cm cng nh mt mi. Cu lng c bit ph bin vi nhng ngi lm vic trong vn phng, cng nhn v sinh vin  nng thn. N cng c chi bi nhiu ngi cao tui trong thnh ph, trong cng vin v sn vn ng nh. Tr chi khng phc tp,  l l do ti sao rt nhiu ngi thch n. Ngoi ra, tr chi cn cc cp i  tr chi l mt cch  giao tip vi bn b, i tc v thc y mi quan h.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>Nhng ng tc n gin khi chicu lng nh dng tay pht - nh vt, chn chy, xoay ngi... li c  ngha tuyt vi i vi sc khe, v l mn th thao chi ngoi tri hoc trong nh, ph hp vi mi la tui, t tr n gi u c th tham gia chi c. Di y l nhng tc dng tuyt vi khi<strong>nh cu lng</strong>bn hy tham kho v nndnh cht thi gian cng ngi thn, bn b tp luyn th dc th thao qua mn cu lng ny.Hng nm S Vn ha, Th thao v Du lch t chc 3-4 gii Cu lng Cc cuc thi u t chc cho mi la tui t 13 tui tr xung ti 60 tui tr ln, n nam, n n, i nam, i n v i nam n.</p>\r\n<p><b>Chi cu lng gip tinh mt, nhanh tay:</b>nh cu lng gip chng ta luyn tinh mt, nhanh tay vi l do cc k n gin. Trong mt trn cu, hai bn u cn phi quan st i th v nhanh chng  cu, bi vy mt cn quan st vt th  tc  cao, khin mt khng ngng gin ra, co li, t  thc y tun hon mu  mt, ci thin chc nng c mt. Trong sut gian di tp luyn, bn s thy tc  phn ng ca mt c ci thin r rt. Vi nhng bn c s thch chi cu n thun,  nhy cm ca th gic cng s tng ln nhanh chng khi cc bn rn luyn u n.</p>\r\n<p><b>Khe tim, gim bo hiu qu khi chi cu lng hng ngy:</b>Mt trn cu lng yu cu ngi chi khng ngng hot ng chn, tay, xoay ngi... c th coi y l mt hot ng c tnh ton din, rt tt cho c th. c bit, cu lng c th gip bn gia tng sc mnh  cc c bp, thc y tun hon mu khp c th, tng cng chc nng h tun hon mu v h h hp. Theo nh thng k, nhp tim ca ngi chi cu lng vi cng  cao l 160-180 nhp mi pht,  ngi chi vi cng  trung bnh l 140- 150 nhp, cng  thp nht l 100-130 nhp. Luyn tp cu lng trong thi gian di gip tim khe mnh, chc nng phi dc ci thin. ng thi, nh cu lng cng c li vi nhng bn ang mun gim bo na nh.</p>\r\n<p>Khi ang nh cu lng, cnh tay, bp tay, chn, vng eo ca bn khng ngng hot ng. V th n sgip bn t chy mt lng calo ng k. Mt thi gian sau, cc bp tht ca bn s sn chc hn rt nhiu.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img src=\"https://sovhtt.langson.gov.vn/sites/sovhtt.langson.gov.vn/files/users/user13/vu-thi-trang.jpg\" alt=\"vu-thi-trang.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"477\" data-widget=\"image\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><a id=\"toc-3\" name=\"toc-3\"></a><b>Cu lng em li li ch cho mi ngi nim vui v sc khe:</b> chnh l mt mn th thao rt d hc nhng li kh tinh thng. Mt ngi mi bt u hc chi cu lng  c th tc khc nhn thy vui th v luyn tp c. Nhng nghin cu v di truyn ch ra rng thng cu th cu lng hot ng tay nhiu hn l cu th bng nm &amp; cng chy nhiu hn cu th bng  trong 60 pht thi u.</p>\r\n<p>Ph n, nam gii v ngay c tr em ai cng c th chi cu lng do  cu lng thng c xem l mn th thao gia nh. Mn th thao ny thch hp chi  nhng ni c din tch nh, trong nh hoc ngoi sn. Ch cn vi chi ph nh nht mi ngi cng c c hi  chi mn th thao ny. Ngoi ra nhng ngi khuyt tt cng c th tham gia chi cu cng vi nhng ngi khc mt cch bnh ng. Cc cuc thi u t chc cho mi la tui t 13 tui tr xung ti 60 tui tr ln, n nam, n n, i nam, i n v i nam n.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span tabindex=\"-1\" contenteditable=\"false\"><img src=\"https://sovhtt.langson.gov.vn/sites/sovhtt.langson.gov.vn/files/users/user13/caulong_0.jpg\" alt=\"caulong_0.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"496\" data-widget=\"image\" /></span></p>\r\n<p><b>Li ch sinh l:</b>Bi tp t va phi n qu sc ty thuc vo kinh nghim ca cu th. y chnh l mt mn chi phi hp nhp nhng gia cc ng tc chy, nhy, dui tay, khi ng, dng li v xoay ngi lm tng cng s sung sc, tnh linh hot, s do dai, trng thi cn bng v sc chu ng ca c th.<b></b>Nhng nghin cu a ra nhng bng chng cu lng l mt trong nhng mn th thao c ch cho h tim mch (s di chuyn nhp nhng lm cho c co bp v th gin tng cng hiu qu bm mu trong h thng tun hon).</p>\r\n<p><a id=\"toc-5\" name=\"toc-5\"></a><b>Li ch tm l:</b>Con ngi khng ngng tm kim s tha mn cho bn thn. Trong cuc sng, cu lng  a ra  tng v mn chi em li s thch th cho la tui u th hoc v thnh nin. Thng qua vic chi cu lng, ngi ln cng cm thy tinh thn phn chn, gim bt s trm cm do  to ra trng thi tinh thn tt hn. Con ngi thng  cp n vn  tui tc v th ngi ta thng hay ni rng \"<i>Bn  qu gi nn khng th lm c iu ny iu kia</i>\". Nhng cu lng l mn th thao thch hp cho mi la tui, v th  bt c tui no vn ng vin cng c th t c thnh tch cao. Cu lng to nn bu khng kh, mi trng x hi  trt nhng cm xc ny.</p>\r\n<p>Trong tim thc, ngi ta c th thc hin nhng c vt  gii ta nhng cm xc th hn, cm ght (nhn mt thy kh a......). Bn canh , tinh thn th thao, thi  lch s vi tnh k lut t gic l nhng bi hc rt ra t mn th thao cu lng hp dn ny.</p>\r\n<p><b>Cu lng l mn th thao tng i d chi v t tn km</b>. V vy phong tro cu lng ngy cng pht trin vi s ngi tham gia tp luyn ngy cng ng o v si ni hn. C th ni cu lng l mn th thao c tnh ton din, rt tt cho c th. Li ch r nht l nh cu lng gip chng ta luyn tinh mt, nhanh tay. Trong mt trn cu, hai bn u cn phi quan st i th v nhanh chng  cu, bi vy mt cn quan st vt th  tc  cao, khin mt khng ngng gin ra, co li, t  thc y tun hon mu  mt, ci thin chc nng c mt. Trong sut thi gian di tp luyn, bn s thy tc  phn ng ca mt c ci thin r rt. Vi nhng bn c s thch chi cu n thun,  nhy cm ca th gic cng s tng ln nhanh chng khi cc bn rn luyn u n.</p>\r\n<p><a id=\"toc-6\" name=\"toc-6\"></a> chi cu lng ng cch v c ch, ngi chi cn lu  khi ng k trc khi vo u trc khi nh cu lng, bn cn khi ng c th, nhng khng nn khi ng qu hng phn. Nh vy rt d b chn thng. Sau khi kt thc trn cu m khng chu th lng c th cng c tc hi nht nh, in hnh l lao lc v nh hng ti cng vic, hc tp ca ngy hm sau.  chun b cho mt trn cu, bn nn khi ng khong 20 pht, sau khi khi ng k, hai bn cng nh nh nhng ri mi dn tr nn quyt lit.</p>\r\n<p>Dng c  chi cu lng khng qu t nn nhiu ngi thch b mn th thao ny. Nhng la chn dng c chi bn cng cn ch  mt s im. Cc bn nn chnqu cu lngc lng cng, thng, khong cch gia cc nhnh lng u nhau, nh vy qu o bay ca cu mi c n nh. Vvt cu lng, cc bn cn c vo trng lng,  ln ca tay cm  chn. Nhng bn c thn hnh to cao thng chn vt c cn chu vi ln. Ngi c lc c tay mnh a dng vt thn cng, nu lc c tay hi yu bn chn vt hi do hn.</p>\r\n<p>Sc khe l nhn t v cng quan trng trong i sng con ngi. Vic luyn tp th dc qu thc c  ngha ln lao. Chng ta c th thy rng tp th dc gip c th ta mnh khe. Khi sc khe tt, con ngi c th lm mi vic bng sc lc, bng kh nng ca mnh. Bn cnh , sc khe cn to ra cho con ngi nhng c hi, nhng tri nghim v phn u ht mnh v tng lai. Rn luyn th dc, th thao gip ta c c th tt, gip tui th ko di. Vic tp th dc cn l phng php hu hiu  gim stress cng nh p lc ca ta trong i sng. Khi khng tp th dc, c th con ngi ru r, i sng tinh thn nng n, mt mi. Tp th dc s cho ta nhng c hi  lm quen cng bao ngi c thi  sng tch cc, vui v, lc quan. Chnh nn tng c th mnh khe l nc thang tuyt diu nng ta ln trong cuc i ny. Hy thc dy v tp th dc thay v nghch in thoi, chm mnh trong th gii ca nhng s li bing bn nh!</p>', '', 1, 8, '2023-12-13 09:30:09', 67, '', '2023-12-13 09:30:09', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2023-12-13 09:30:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 1, 0, '', '', 1, 3, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', '', '');
